# Team Expansion and Reddit Lead Generation Plan

This plan covers two main objectives:
1. **Team Onboarding**: Enabling a new member to interact with the Gravity Claw agent fleet and join the development environment.
2. **Reddit Lead Generation**: Implementing the automated discovery and outreach strategy defined in the R&D report.

## Proposed Changes

### [Gravity Claw]

#### [MODIFY] [.env](file:///Users/tahmidnur/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/theresidentialaddress/agents/gravity-claw/.env)
- Append the new team member's Telegram ID to `AUTHORIZED_TELEGRAM_USER_ID`.
- Update `HQ_GROUP_ID` if a new coordination group is created.

#### [MODIFY] [src/index.ts](file:///Users/tahmidnur/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/theresidentialaddress/agents/gravity-claw/src/index.ts)
- Update `markBtmSystemPrompt` and `asanSystemPrompt` to include instructions for the Reddit monitoring and lead scoring workflow.

#### [NEW] [reddit_onboarding.md](file:///Users/tahmidnur/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/theresidentialaddress/agents/gravity-claw/reddit_onboarding.md)
- Create a quick-start guide for the team member on how to interact with the agents on Telegram.

### [Research & Development]

#### [NEW] [src/tools/reddit.ts](file:///Users/tahmidnur/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/theresidentialaddress/agents/gravity-claw/src/tools/reddit.ts)
- Implement a `search_reddit` tool that uses `search_web` to find relevant threads in targeted subreddits (`r/stripe`, `r/digitalnomad`, etc.).
- Add logic to extract thread snippets and qualify leads based on keywords like "KYC", "residential address", "restricted".

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Test the `search_reddit` tool with specific queries to ensure it returns relevant thread links and snippets.
- Verify that the whitelisting logic in [src/index.ts](file:///Users/tahmidnur/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/theresidentialaddress/agents/gravity-claw/src/index.ts) correctly processes the updated `AUTHORIZED_TELEGRAM_USER_ID`.

### Manual Verification
1. **Team Member Test**: Have the new member send a message to `@asanbot` or `@markbtmbot` on Telegram and confirm they get a response.
2. **Reddit Strategy Run**: Ask Asan to "Generate daily Reddit lead report" and verify it drafts responses according to the "Value-First" strategy.
